{"tid":2172833,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星島日報：習近平於8月26日南下深圳，親自視察蓮塘口岸，鄭月娥女士獲傳召陪伴","createTime":"2020-08-25T01:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T04:00:42.000Z","uid":155095,"like":258,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":135,"replies":[{"pid":"b7daa34c2c6abf523fc3e3287ed389c5d746d0aa","tid":2172833,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:30:19.000Z","msg":"蘋果source: <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/2AEMHBAYY5HEVLSQ5B4FPX7FHM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2F2AEMHBAYY5HEVLSQ5B4FPX7FHM%2F&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3Sbllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=22479c7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200825%2F2AEMHBAYY5HEVLSQ5B4FPX7FHM%2F&h=11b17462\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200825/2AEMHBAYY5HEVLSQ5B4FPX7FHM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2020年8月26日</strong>是深圳經濟特區成立40周年，《<strong>星島日報</strong>》引述消息報道，<span class=\"red\">中共總書記習近平</span>將南下參加慶祝活動，<span class=\"green\">行政長官林鄭月娥</span>也會獲邀出席 &hellip;略&hellip; 時事評論員指，習屆時講話十分重要，需觀察到底他會依已故中共領導人鄧小平的改革方針走，還是要背棄鄧的主張、關門倒退來打自己人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jv1HFhG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJv1HFhG.jpg&h=68612785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據知習近平屆時將會參觀新開通的<strong>蓮塘口岸</strong> &hellip;略&hellip; 政府新聞處昨稱，林鄭月娥明日將會與政務司長張建宗等官員赴深圳蓮塘口岸出席開通儀式，即日來回。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IHH34L2JR4IMGJ5FWERQPARPUY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIHH34L2JR4IMGJ5FWERQPARPUY.gif&h=203b123d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2012年12月，習近平甫上任中共總書記一職，第一個離京視察的地方就是廣東 &hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"0ba5626e1761574abb9c291ec217a99f75bd4b02","tid":2172833,"uid":290883,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:49:04.000Z","msg":"奉旨三陪！"},{"pid":"da4b99c2be9cc4ea99ad544604ec678652055773","tid":2172833,"uid":214502,"like":128,"dislike":3,"score":125,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:50:20.000Z","msg":"老婆走左佬要搵下屬出火<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3e6e073d38bf814f88481f8e365cbd49feadf33","tid":2172833,"uid":3241,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:51:03.000Z","msg":"鄭匪月娥呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"19eb6d1885f03004d71c8f5e2c92c1fe1872f24a","tid":2172833,"uid":344567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:52:26.000Z","msg":"翻牌子"},{"pid":"ac3d30ea284a1883e8dceb5873ffe47eaea43293","tid":2172833,"uid":293677,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:52:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有種落黎香港"},{"pid":"bec57adf2f5b4a5eb29633d04d9f99c7b7a1e194","tid":2172833,"uid":281492,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:52:47.000Z","msg":"係雞係公廁"},{"pid":"8b5094daf90c056d71875b80eaf29fe4f74d8c64","tid":2172833,"uid":238920,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:52:56.000Z","msg":"習種始終念念不忘月娥<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1284258/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1284258/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"b8432c9c6217207070314e518472c1d405e7aec2","tid":2172833,"uid":293677,"like":10,"dislike":100,"score":-90,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:54:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ifun01.com/images/2018/02/04/17/0501_HlkjCx_gNXpf5.jpg!r800x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ifun01.com%2Fimages%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F17%2F0501_HlkjCx_gNXpf5.jpg%21r800x0.jpg&h=c13f4148&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0f09a758adb9226ca9b2c5e49d6cddaa825601b4","tid":2172833,"uid":7323,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:54:40.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">肉便器</span>"},{"pid":"c7d2b7c643353e0cac81535