AYY5HEVLSQ5B4FPX7FHM/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>2020年8月26日</strong>是深圳經濟特區成立40周年，《<strong>星島日報</strong>》引述消息報道，<span class=\"red\">中共總書記習近平</span>將南下參加慶祝活動，<span class=\"green\">行政長官林鄭月娥</span>也會獲邀出席 &hellip;略&hellip; 時事評論員指，習屆時講話十分重要，需觀察到底他會依已故中共領導人鄧小平的改革方針走，還是要背棄鄧的主張、關門倒退來打自己人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jv1HFhG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJv1HFhG.jpg&h=68612785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據知習近平屆時將會參觀新開通的<strong>蓮塘口岸</strong> &hellip;略&hellip; 政府新聞處昨稱，林鄭月娥明日將會與政務司長張建宗等官員赴深圳蓮塘口岸出席開通儀式，即日來回。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IHH34L2JR4IMGJ5FWERQPARPUY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIHH34L2JR4IMGJ5FWERQPARPUY.gif&h=203b123d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2012年12月，習近平甫上任中共總書記一職，第一個離京視察的地方就是廣東 &hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T03:54:04.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"large\">[size=4]呢張圖真係極力有潛質做旗幡！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d4c5788ec15813d7f4642b3a3ef1fffcfdd14a","tid":2172833,"uid":249260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:00:36.000Z","msg":"維尼去親邊度<br />\n邊度就會仆街<br />\n今次輪到廣東啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f52e17f2dddbfca95212ac19e1e2a607ff5f74ab","tid":2172833,"uid":216810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:02:27.000Z","msg":"伴遊服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0577e21452dd4a77d8aadd36692caca3c8348b92","tid":2172833,"uid":210088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T04:04:13.000Z","msg":"我又諗起你老婆<img src=\"/assets/fa